sub_title: English Editor at the Faculty of Humanities, University of Amsterdam.
summary: Historian devoted to writing accessible, entertaining, but well-researched pieces whenever time allows it, not just within the field of history but also stretching to prehistory and palaeoanthropology. I currently work as English editor within the Faculty of Humanities at the University of Amsterdam, and I also work as associate editor & contributor for Ancient History Encyclopedia in my spare time.
